{"TopicId":155424,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Option To Remove Top Of Engines","CreatedByName":"BananaTime101","CreatedById":139798,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T19:33:06Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"BananaTime101","CreatedById":139798,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T19:33:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn KSP when trying to make engine clusters, sometimes you have to use the move gizmo to get them right. However, sometimes you can\u0027t move it all the way out otherwise the annoying top of the engine pokes out. What I\u0027m suggesting is there to be a left click option on engines to remove this piece. (If even possible) This is what i\u0027m taking about.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022D3rXwpP.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/D3rXwpP.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Banana\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frozen_Heart","CreatedById":118627,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T19:47:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFrom the look of that porkjet engine overhaul this was going to be a thing.... until the devs left.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably won\u0027t get this now. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wjolcz","CreatedById":39636,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-23T00:35:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe lack of tankbutts would be pretty amazing to have. So many more possibilities!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Choctofliatrio2.0","CreatedById":154657,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-23T12:42:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh boy, the tankbutt debate again. I remember when this was a hot topic on the forums... that take me back.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile I wouldn\u0027t mind it, it\u0027s never really been a problem for me. I\u0027ve never had to build a rocket with tanks too big for their engines.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frozen_Heart","CreatedById":118627,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-23T22:37:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222931522\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155424\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485175334\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154657\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Choctofliatrio2.0\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, Choctofliatrio2.0 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh boy, the tankbutt debate again. I remember when this was a hot topic on the forums... that take me back.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile I wouldn\u0027t mind it, it\u0027s never really been a problem for me. I\u0027ve never had to build a rocket with tanks too big for their engines.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s mainly a problem if you try to cluster lots of little engines spacex style.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gaarst","CreatedById":126740,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-23T22:49:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes remove these stupid tankbutts and make all engines surface attachable please. I take it we\u0027ll never get an actual choice between different\u00A0engines for the same usage, at least give us the ability\u00A0to make clusters.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-23T22:50:05Z\u0022 title=\u002201/23/2017 10:50  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 23, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Gaarst\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-23T23:22:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222932176\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155424\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485211765\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022126740\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gaarst\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n26 minutes ago, Gaarst said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntankbutts\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222931152\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155424\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485131704\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002239636\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Veeltch\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 hours ago, Veeltch said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntankbutts\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222931522\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155424\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485175334\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154657\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Choctofliatrio2.0\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Choctofliatrio2.0 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntankbutt\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve been a member of this forum for a while now and had no idea what a tankbutt was referring to... I saw this thread today and will have to admit, I snickered at the whole tankbutt concept. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003EI\u0027ve seen it thrown around here and there all over the forum, but for some reason, it has always made me snicker... I guess it\u0027s too much like the old Wayne\u0027s World thing coming back to haunt me... (hehehe, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/126740-gaarst/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022126740\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/126740-gaarst/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Gaarst\u003C/a\u003E said \u0022tankbutt!) Thank you all for the good laugh on a day when everything else has seemed to go awry!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}